          I am a student at Fudan University, pursuing a Bachelor of Engineering in Software Engineering. I'm seeking internship opportunities in Quant Development & AI Research.
        </p>
        <Button title='More about me' class='w-fit self-end' href='/about' style='ahead' />
      </Section> 
      {
        allPostsByDate.length > 0 && (
